<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Welcome to Hackwarts</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  </head>
  <body>
    <header>
      <div class="container">
          <h1>Welcome to Hackwarts</h1>
        <nav>
          <ul>
            <li><a href="/login">Login</a></li>
            <li><a href="/register">Register</a></li>
            <li><a href="/aboutus">About Us</a></li>
          </ul>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </header>
    <main>
      <div class="header-image">
        <img src="/images/hogwarts-castle.jpg" alt="Hogwarts" class="header-image">
      </div>
      <div class="container">
        <div class="grid">
          <div class="content">
            <h1>Welcome to the Hackwarts School of Cybersecurity and Hacking,</h1>
            <div class="text">
              <p>The Hackwarts School of Cybersecurity and Hacking is a prestigious institution that trains the most talented and ambitious hackers in the wizarding world. Its curriculum includes courses in cryptography, penetration testing, social engineering, and malware analysis.</p>
              <p style="margin-top: 1em">Here are the four houses:</p>
              <ul style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; margin-left: 3em;">
                <li><a>Hackledore</a></li>
                <li><a>Malwarein</a></li>
                <li><a>Cryptoclaws</a></li>
                <li><a>Phisherpuff</a></li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="image">
            <img src="/images/hogwarts-logo.jpg" alt="Image">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="container">
        <div class="grid">
          <div class="image">
            <img src="/images/gryffindor.jpg" alt="Image">
          </div>
          <div class="content">
            <h1>Hackledore</h1>
            <div class="text">
              <p>The Hackledore house is named after the famous hacker and cybersecurity expert, Albus Hackledore. Its members are known for their wisdom, resourcefulness, and ability to think outside the box. They excel at finding vulnerabilities in complex systems and devising clever solutions to exploit them.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="container">
        <div class="grid">
          <div class="content">
            <h1>Malwarein</h1>
            <div class="text">
              <p>The Malwarein house is full of mischievous and cunning hackers who specialize in creating and spreading malware. They take great pleasure in infecting unsuspecting systems and watching chaos ensue. Their motto is "We infect, you suffer!"</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="image">
            <img src="/images/slytherin.jpg" alt="Image">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="container">
        <div class="grid">
          <div class="image">
            <img src="/images/ravenclaw.jpg" alt="Image">
          </div>
          <div class="content">
            <h1>Cryptoclaws</h1>
            <div class="text">
              <p>The Cryptoclaws house is named after the powerful encryption algorithms used to protect sensitive data. Its members are experts in cryptography and data protection, and are dedicated to keeping information safe from prying eyes. Their motto is "We lock it up, you can't get in!"</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="container">
        <div class="grid">
          <div class="content">
            <h1>Phisherpuff</h1>
            <div class="text">
              <p>The Phisherpuff house is the most charming and persuasive of all the cybersecurity houses. Its members are skilled at social engineering and phishing attacks, luring unsuspecting users into divulging sensitive information. Their motto is "We don't break in, we get invited!"</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="image">
            <img src="/images/hufflepuff.jpg" alt="Image">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
    <footer>
      <div class="container">
        <p>&copy; Hackwarts School of Cybersecurity and Hacking</p>
      </div>
    </footer>
    <script src="/js/script.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
